Prompt: Class Inheritance System with Parent-Child Relationships (Unreal Engine Style)
I want to build a complete class inheritance system exactly like Unreal Engine, where each Actor class can have a parent class and child classes. You can create a parent class, assign it to other classes, or right-click in the Content Browser to create a child class from any existing class. The most important part is that when we update a parent class, all changes must automatically reflect in all child classes while preserving child-specific overrides.
IMPORTANT: Please consider the current architecture and what we've already implemented:

Actor system with components
Blueprint/Node editor
Content Browser
Component system
Variables and structures
Project save/load system
JSON storage

The inheritance system should integrate seamlessly with all existing systems.

Core Concept (Unreal Engine Style)
Class Hierarchy:
Actor (Base Engine Class)
├── Character Pawn (Engine Class)
│   ├── PlayerCharacter (Your Parent Class)
│   │   ├── WarriorCharacter (Child Class)
│   │   ├── MageCharacter (Child Class)
│   │   └── ArcherCharacter (Child Class)
│   │
│   └── EnemyCharacter (Your Parent Class)
│       ├── ZombieEnemy (Child Class)
│       ├── SkeletonEnemy (Child Class)
│       └── BossEnemy (Child Class)
│
├── Item (Your Parent Class)
│   ├── Weapon (Child Class)
│   │   ├── Sword (Child of Weapon)
│   │   ├── Axe (Child of Weapon)
│   │   └── Bow (Child of Weapon)
│   │
│   └── Consumable (Child Class)
│       ├── HealthPotion (Child of Consumable)
│       └── ManaPotion (Child of Consumable)
│
└── Vehicle (Your Parent Class)
    ├── Car (Child Class)
    └── Motorcycle (Child Class)
Key Rules:

Child inherits EVERYTHING from parent (components, variables, nodes, properties)
Child can OVERRIDE parent values (but keeps parent structure)
Child can ADD new components, variables, nodes (extends parent)
Child CANNOT REMOVE parent's components or variables
Parent changes propagate to ALL children automatically
Overrides are preserved when parent updates


